OL,3,CCelebrations held at grand opening of
OL,4,COxford's first Hindu temple
OL,6,FCelebrations have been held in Oxford
OL,7,Ffor the "once-in-a-generation" opening
OL,8,Fof the city's first official Hindu
OL,9,Ftemple.
OL,11,FThe Oxford Hindu Mandir & Community
OL,12,FCentre welcomed visitors for its grand
OL,13,Fopening on Sunday.
OL,15,FDignitaries and faith leaders also
OL,16,Fattended to conduct traditional
OL,17,Fceremonies to bless the building.
OL,19,FA programme of events saw widespread
OL,20,Fcelebrations, including prayer, music
OL,21,Fand dance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
