OL,3,CCelebrations held at grand opening of
OL,4,COxford's first Hindu temple
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMembers of the Hindu community in
OL,12,FOxford had previously congregated in
OL,13,Fschool halls and community centres.
OL,15,FBut, with the centre now open, leaders
OL,16,Fare aiming to offer regular puja,
OL,17,Ffestival programmes, language and
OL,18,Fmusic classes, and space for community
OL,19,Forganisations.
