OL,3,CCelebrations held at grand opening of
OL,4,COxford's first Hindu temple
OL,6,F"Despite being one of Oxford's largest
OL,7,Fand fastest-growing faith communities,
OL,8,FHindus have never had a dedicated
OL,9,Ftemple and cultural centre," according
OL,10,Fto the centre's official website.
OL,12,F"This project establishes a lasting
OL,13,Fspiritual foundation for our community
OL,14,Fand future generations."
